            <description><![CDATA[
                <p><a href="http://jberger.github.io">Joel Berger</a> wrote <a href="http://blogs.perl.org/users/joel_berger/2016/04/reflections-on-test2.html">a blog post reflecting on
Test2</a>
<a href="https://github.com/exodist">Chad Granum&#39;s (Exodist)</a>
new core test library. (<a href="http://metacpan.org/pod/Test2">Read more about Test2 on Metacpan</a>).</p>

<p>In his post, Joel explains the rationale behind Test2, the history that
has led to this situation, and the path forward getting Test2 into the
Perl core.</p>

<p>Read Joel&#39;s post on blogs.perl.org:
<a href="http://blogs.perl.org/users/joel_berger/2016/04/reflections-on-test2.html">http://blogs.perl.org/users/joel_berger/2016/04/reflections-on-test2.html</a></p>

